  "texts": [
    "Informed by the sociotechnical insights of the iSTS framework, we developed a hierarchical HCAI (hHCAI) approach, offering a structured extension of current HCAI practices from a broader sociotechnical perspective.",
    "This approach comprehensively addresses gaps in HCAI practices by integrating sociotechnical considerations.",
    "Finally, we provide recommendations for further enhancing the iSTS framework and implementing the hHCAI approach.",
    "These recommendations aim to mitigate AI's potential negative societal impacts while ensuring the development and use of AI technologies align with human values and societal needs.",
    "This paper adopts a qualitative approach to reviewing seminal works in STS and HCAI."
  ],
